That champion is simply obnoxious if I'm not bot lane or if I'm not playing Morgana. Typically ends up 15/4 with his ult executing at 50% health, and there's very very little anyone can do about it. Very unforgiving champion, if he doesn't chain his ult in one team fight, he only has to do it once to change the game.

I miss Ornn, Ivern, Warwick rework level of champ design. {{sticker:cass-cry}}

